messages.message: Hey England, how're you doing? Are you down for an alliance to secure both our positioning for the mid-game?
Hey Italy! Would you be up for keeping in touch and potentially sharing information if either of us come across anything that might be useful?
Hey-hey-hey! Big fan of a solid EG and would absolutely be down to work together. What are you thinking?
Awesome. I'd love to see a convoy into Norway, maybe with support? What do you wanna do with Belgium?
Either way, I think I'm gonna open a standard way and then I'll see what I can do about bouncing Russia out of Sweden in the fall
You want a convoy to NWY? Hmmmm, I was thinking of a convoy to BEL but I would be open to an army in NWY (on the condition SWE gets bounced)
Sorry for the late reply! Lost track of time but Im here
Deal!
No worries!
Awesome!
But I agree!
Looking forward to this :)

Might as well spend the extra time to talk some more

Still all good. Have to cover Munich because of France. Should be able to stop Russia out of Sweden though. You wanna convoy to Norway and move NWG into Barents?

Wanna convoy into Norway and then take Belgium next year?
Hopefully you can turn it around!
I would prefer to take BEL this turn
I need to cover Munich because of France, but you can bounce him out of Belgium with North and then he won't get a build and will be easy to take out next year
